[h2 
	" Cheat Codes
	$LF
	[a id=heading-3992 
	]a
]h2
[p 
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"While playing a level, type "BALDRIC" to activate cheat mode. This will reset your score to zero. While holding Left-Shift, you can now type one of the following:
	$LF
]p
[ul 
	[li 
		" R xx - where xx is the number of a room to jump to (01~45)
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" H - maximum health, food and drink
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" K - get all keys except for the tower key
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" W - get full weapons
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" C - get 10 coins
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[p 
	[br 
	]br
	" 
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
]p
[h2 
	" Faster Speed
	$LF
	[a id=heading-4371 
	]a
]h2
[p 
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"You can press "+" to increase the game's speed. This can be abused for speedrunning purposes.
	$LF
	[br 
	]br
	" 
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
